---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Men haqimda — TZIM Blog">
  <div class="container page">
    <a href="/" class="back">← Orqaga</a>

    <h1>Bu kim yozadi<br>va nima uchun</h1>

    <div class="prose">
      <p>
        Mening ismim [Ism]. Men infratuzilma bilan shug'ullanaman — serverlar, konteynerlar,
        avtomatlashtirish. Bu blog — men topgan yechimlarni saqlaydigan joy,
        qayta izlamaslik uchun.
      </p>

      <p>
        Ko'pchilik maqolalar bitta jumladan boshlanadi: <em>"men bunga bir necha soat sarfladim,
        siz 10 daqiqada bajarasiz"</em>. Hech qanday bo'sh gap yo'q, faqat ishlaydigan buyruqlar va konfiglar.
      </p>

      <h2>Stek</h2>
      <p>
        Proxmox VE, Docker, Linux (Debian/Ubuntu), PostgreSQL, Nginx/Traefik,
        GitHub Actions, Ansible, PowerDNS.
      </p>

      <h2>Bog'lanish</h2>
      <p>
        Telegram: <a href="https://t.me/yourhandle">@yourhandle</a><br>
        GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/yourname">github.com/yourname</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  .page {
    max-width: 680px;
    padding-top: 3rem;
    padding-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .back {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-decoration: none;
    display: inline-block;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .back:hover { color: var(--text); }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.2;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
</style>
